- Id (Guid, PK)
- ProjectId (Guid, FK → Project)
- Name (string) — user defines: "development", "staging", "production" etc.
- SortOrder (int)
- Color (string) — hex from predefined palette:
    development → #6E7CF8
    test        → #2ECC71
    staging     → #F5A623
    production  → #E74C3C
    default     → #9B59B6
- ApiKey (string, Guid.NewGuid().ToString("N"), unique index)
- CreatedAt (DateTime UTC)

### FeatureFlag
- Id (Guid, PK)
- ProjectId (Guid, FK → Project)
- Name (string, slug format: [a-z0-9-] only, unique per project)
- Description (string, max 500)
- FlagType (enum): Release=0, Operational=1, Permission=2
- CreatedByUserId (string, FK → ApplicationUser)
- CreatedAt / UpdatedAt (DateTime UTC)
- IsArchived (bool, default false)
- LastSeenAt (DateTime? UTC)

### FeatureFlagEnvironmentState
- Id (Guid, PK)
- FeatureFlagId (Guid, FK)
- ProjectEnvironmentId (Guid, FK)
- IsEnabled (bool, default false)
- EnabledForUserIds (string) — comma-separated
- EnabledForUserEmails (string) — comma-separated
- UserMatchMode (enum): UserId=0, UserEmail=1, Both=2
- RolloutPercentage (int, 0-100, default 100)
- UpdatedAt (DateTime UTC)
- UpdatedByUserId (string, FK)

### ProjectMember
- Id (Guid, PK)
- ProjectId (Guid, FK → Project)
- UserId (string, FK → ApplicationUser)
- Role (enum): Owner=0, Member=1
- AddedAt (DateTime UTC)
- AddedByUserId (string)
- Unique index on (ProjectId, UserId)

### FlagAuditLog
- Id (Guid, PK)
- FeatureFlagId (Guid, FK)
- ProjectEnvironmentId (Guid, FK)
- PerformedByUserId (string)
- ChangeType (enum): Created, Enabled, Disabled, StrategyUpdated, Archived
- PreviousValueJson (string)
- NewValueJson (string)
- CreatedAt (DateTime UTC)

### FlagEvaluationMetric
- Id (Guid, PK)
- FeatureFlagId (Guid, FK)
- ProjectEnvironmentId (Guid, FK)
- EvaluatedAt (DateTime UTC) — truncated to 5-minute bucket
- TrueCount (long)
- FalseCount (long)

